  <brief_title>Antifungal Effects of rhGM-CSF in Patients After Allo-HSCT</brief_title>
  <official_title>Antifungal Effects of Recombinant Human Granulocyte Macrophage Colony Stimulating Factor in Patients After Allogeneic Hematopoietic Stem Cell Transplantation</official_title>
