  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Allogenic hematological stem cell transplantation(HSCT) patients.

          -  No serious damage to heart, liver and kidney function(TBIL≤34μmol/L, Cr≤120μmol/L, a
             normal EF).

          -  Informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients were receiving anti-fungal treatment with proven SFI before transplantation.

          -  Allergic to rhGM-CSF or rhG-CSF.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
